  EffectDiscription_JPN: 
  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Hand] [Main] If you don't have any Digimon other than
    Digimon with [Dark Masters]\_in their texts, you may play this card with the
    play cost reduced by 5. At turn end, delete the Digimon this effect played.\n[On
    Play] [When Attacking] 1 of your opponent's Digimon and 1 of their Tamers can't
    suspend until their turn ends.\n[All Turns] This Digimon can only digivolve into
    [Apocalymon].\n[On Deletion] If you have no blue face-up security cards, place
    this Digimon face up as the bottom security card."
